<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Thank You Email</title>
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        background-color: #000000;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        padding: 30px;
        border-left: 5px solid transparent;
        color: #ffffff;
        border-image: linear-gradient(
            90deg,
            #ffb23f,
            #ffb23f 13%,
            #ff5e71 100%,
            #ff5e71 0
          )
          1;
      }
      h1 {
        color: #ffffff;
        font-size: 26px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      p {
        color: #ffffff;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 20px;
        border-top: 1px solid #ffffff;
        padding-top: 10px;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #ffffff;
      }
      .highlight {
        color: #ffffff;
        font-weight: 700;
      }
      img {
        max-width: 100%; /* Make the image responsive */
        height: auto; /* Maintain aspect ratio */
        margin-bottom: 20px; /* Space below the image */
        border-radius: 5px; /* Optional: round corners */
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
        <img
          src="https://quantify.s3.us-east-005.backblazeb2.com/images/QaLogo.png"
          alt="Your Image Description"
          style="background-color: black; border-radius: 5px; opacity: 0.5 text-align: center justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto; display: block;"
        />
          <h1>Thank You!</h1>
          <p>Dear <span class="highlight text-gradient">{{NAME}}</span>,</p>
      <p>
        Thank you for reaching out to us! We have received your message and our
        team will get back to you as soon as possible.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you have any additional information or questions, feel free to reply
        to this email.
      </p>
      <p>Thank you for your patience!</p>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>Best regards,<br />Quentify It team</p>
      </div>
      <img
        src="https://quantify.s3.us-east-005.backblazeb2.com/images/Communication.png"
        alt="Your Image Description"
        style="width: 100%; opacity: 0.5"
      />
      <div class="footer" style="margin: 0; padding: 0">
        <p>
          Email:- <a style="color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none;" href="mailto:quantifyitagency@gmail.com"> quantifyitagency@gmail.com</a>
        </p>
        <p>Phone:- <a style="color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none;" href="tel:+1234567890"> +44 7425 824506</a></p>
        <p>
          Website:-
          <a style="color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none;" href="https://quantifyitagency.com target="_blank"
            > quantifyitagency.com</a
          >
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
